    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I've digged in go-ethereum code and found that the only way to get an error with this message is here: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/c5dc61c62dabf88091943e02ad309448df26feaa/core/vm/evm.go#L474. It seems that the gas estimation for creation doesn't take into consideration the cost of storing the bytecode.",
